{"tid":1038951,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【財政預算案】再為DSE學校考生繳考試費　向基層學生派錢2500元","createTime":"2019-02-27T05:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T05:27:31.000Z","uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c8220e17480167a812e544527ecdda339f9af89e","tid":1038951,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:24:33.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波今日早上11時開始發表2019/20年度《財政預算案》，稱會推出一系列利民紓困措施，包括向有需要的學生一次過發放2,500元津貼，支援學習需要，開支約8億9,000萬元；並為參加2020年香港中學文憑考試的學校考生代繳考試費，開支約1億6,000萬元。<br />\n<br />\n又有2500<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c37dfc7df0841c98511bfed30cec377093dd2ac","tid":1038951,"uid":224452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:26:37.000Z","msg":"幾時派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708ea3972e19499e274bae6257e0af80165da978","tid":1038951,"uid":31094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:27:31.000Z","msg":"咁就用10億"}]}